This is the seventh release candidate of Hastymail2. We are happy to announce that this
release contains many fixes and updates since the last release candidate and is the
best Hastymail version yet. To see a detailed list of the updates contained in this
release you can read the CHANGES file in the download or view it online at:

http://hastymail.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/hastymail/trunk/hastymail2/CHANGES?view=markup

Thanks to everyone for your support. We value all feedback and
comments so if you are interested in helping with the Hastymail project 
you can find many ways to get in touch with us at the contact page of our website:

http://www.hastymail.org/contact_us/
